<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Samuel Jeffries</h1>
      <h3>About Me</h3>
      
      <hr>
      
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag "MC Zelda.jpg", width: "300", alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>
          
          <div class="skills">
           <% @skills.each  do |skill| %>
           <div class="skill">
                          <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
             <div class="progress">
               <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
               role="progressbar"
               aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
               aria-valuemax="100"
               style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%;"
               >
                 
               </div>
           </div>
             </div>
             
           <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-8">
          <p>I am a student of Kearns High School. I've been in the higher courses of school (GT, AP, Honors) for my whole life, and I'm generally an overall chill guy. Oh, and I can program. I only, recently started *really* programming on June 12, 2017 and, hopefully since then I've decided to not be lazy and actually continue.</p>
          
          <p>I enjoy many video games, usually retro ones, but I do enjoy many newer games as well. This may be important to note, when looking at the games I have made.</p>
          
          <p>
            <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
            >
              Job History
            </button>
            <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
            >
              Education
            </button>
          </p>
          
          <p>
            <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
              <div class="card card-block">
                I have not worked anywhere in the past.
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
          
          <p>
            <div class="collapse" id="education">
              <div class="card card-block">
                Whittier Elementary School
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Thomas Jeffries Junior High School
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Kearns High School
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </div>
</div>